    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor Survival 550lbs Tactical Paracord Rope is a US Military Mil-Spec Type III cord in accordance with specification MIL-C-5040H. This 550 Type III Parachute Cord a must-have key component for every day carry to all survival kits, bug out bags, camping essential kits and even hiking gear alike, as you never know what might pop up on you in the great outdoors. Available in a wide ride of patterns, from wildness camouflage to bright and reflective, easy to spot rescue colors. All ASR Outdoor 550 Tactical Paracord is made from 7 Stands of 100% Nylon genuine Mil-Spec 550lb parachute cord. The same stuff used by the US Military. It has a breaking strength of 550lbs with a working load of 220lbs</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Survival 550 Type III Mil-Spec Tactical Paracord Rope (Many Lengths)</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor Survival 550lbs Tactical Paracord Rope is a US Military Mil-Spec Type III cord in accordance with specification MIL-C-5040H. This 550 Type III Parachute Cord a must-have key component for every day carry to all survival kits, bug out bags, camping essential kits and even hiking gear alike, as you never know what might pop up on you in the great outdoors. Available in a wide ride of patterns, from wildness camouflage to bright and reflective, easy to spot rescue colors.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"