/strong> DC-50-154</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 180525537745</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>All ASR Outdoor 550 Tactical Paracord is made from 7 Stands of 100% Nylon genuine Mil-Spec 550lb parachute cord. The same stuff used by the US Military. It has a breaking strength of 550lbs with a working load of 220lbs. The overall thickness of the parachute cord line is 5/32&quot; diameter and has a consistent stretch of 10% elongation underweight in lab tests.</p>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor Survival 550lbs Tactical Parachute Cord is extremely strong while being lightweight and compact. Available in multiple lengths up to 500 feet there is an option that is right for your prepper, survival, or boy scout needs. Genuine Military Grade Tactical Paracord is versatile and handy. Designed to take a beating and keep on working, never leave home without it.</p>\n  <p>Beef up your bug out bag with the ASR Outdoor Survival 550 Type III Mil-Spec Tactical Paracord Rope.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
